    "en": {
      "title": "Another delay in ship arrival",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro Gas Company announced today (05) that the vessel carrying 3,724 metric tons of gas, which was supposed to arrive in the country between July 6 and 8, will arrive late due to inclement weather.",
        "Lidro has announced that the vessel will be delayed due to unexpected weather changes and rough seas.",
        "The gas export will be based on an agreement signed between Litro and the World Bank to bring 100,000 metric tons of gas to the country."
      ],
